                                your horizons, build your network, and advance your career.
                            </p>
                            <div className="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start mb-8">
                                <PrimaryButton
                                    onClick={() => handleDiscoveryNavigation()}
                                    className="px-8 py-3 text-lg font-semibold font-inter"
                                >
                                    Discover Events
                                </PrimaryButton>
                                <button
                                    onClick={() => navigate('/about')}
                                    className="px-8 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-lg hover:border-gray-400 transition-colors font-inter"
                                >
                                    Learn More
                                </button>
                            </div>
                            <div className="flex items-center gap-8 text-sm text-gray-500 font-inter">
                                <div className="flex items-center gap-2">
